<HL>
   Homestake Set
   To Buy Corona
   For $395 Million
   ----
   By Larry M. Greenberg and Karen Blumenthal
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
03/16/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A16
</SO>
<CO>
   DBC.A HM ICR T.ICR
</CO>
